Description:
Personally owned by an employee or affiliate of the
        corporation or enterprise.
Owned by a partner of the corporation or enterprise.

Owned by a customer of the corporation or
        enterprise.

Owned by an entity that has no known
        relationship with the victim organization.

A value used to indicate that this attribute is
        extended and the actual value is provided using the
        corresponding ext-* attribute.  See Section 5.1.1 of [RFC7970].
